<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy - Concepts" %>

<div class="container-narrow">
  <header class="page-header" style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="/" class="logo">Concepts</a>
    <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #A8A29E;">Effective as of <%= Date.today.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
  </header>

  <article style="color: #57534E; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px;">
    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Concepts is operated by Tsimafei Launik as a sole proprietorship (jednoosobowa działalność gospodarcza) registered in Poland.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">2. What We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect your email address when you sign up via Apple Sign In. We also collect your timezone to personalize your experience and ensure daily concept limits reset at the correct time for you.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Concepts is not intended for children under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">3. Why We Collect It</h2>
      <p>Your email is used to create and manage your account. Your timezone helps us deliver daily concept limits that reset at the right time for you. We do not use your data for tracking or unrelated promotions.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">4. Where Your Data Is Stored</h2>
      <p>Your data is stored in a secure database. We do not share your data with third parties except as necessary to provide the service (e.g., Apple Sign In, OpenAI for concept generation).</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Your account data will be retained until you delete your account. You may request deletion anytime through the app settings or by contacting us.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">6. Analytics</h2>
      <p>We may use analytics tools to understand general trends in how people use Concepts. Any analytics tools we use are privacy-focused and do not track personal data or share information with third parties. All data is aggregated and anonymized.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">7. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We may use minimal session cookies via Rails to enable core functionality. These cookies do not track or identify you across other sites.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You can request to view or delete your personal data by emailing <a href="mailto:tim@concepts.app" style="text-decoration: underline;">tim@concepts.app</a> or by using the account deletion feature in the app settings.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">9. AI-Generated Content</h2>
      <p>Concepts generated by our AI are for educational and reflection purposes only. We do not collect or infer any sensitive personal traits based on the concepts you generate or interact with.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">10. Legal Basis</h2>
      <p>Your explicit consent is our legal basis for collecting your email address and timezone under GDPR.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; margin-bottom: 8px;">11. Updates</h2>
      <p>This policy may change. Updates will be reflected here with a revised date.</p>
    </section>

    <footer style="padding-top: 24px; margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #E7E5E4; font-size: 12px; color: #A8A29E;">
      This document is written in English. In the case of translation, the English version will prevail.
    </footer>
  </article>
</div>
